The approach for this problem find the string with the shortest length and use this to add characters until this length , then add remaining characters of the larger string to this new string and return it.



class Solution {
    public String mergeAlternately(String word1, String word2) {

        StringBuffer str = new StringBuffer();

        int min_length = Math.min(word1.length(), word2.length());

        for(int i = 0;i < min_length; i++)
        {
            str.append(word1.charAt(i));
            str.append(word2.charAt(i));

        }

        for(int i = min_length; i< word1.length();i++)
        {
            str.append(word1.charAt(i));
        }
        for(int i = min_length; i< word2.length();i++)
        {
            str.append(word2.charAt(i));
        }


        return str.toString();
        
    }
}
